#. <section class="sutta" id="sn38.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn38.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga"
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 1. Nibbānapañhāsutta → nibbānasuttaṃ (bj) | nibbānaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn38.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Nibbānapañhāsutta"
msgstr "1. A Question About Extinguishment"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn38.1:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā sāriputto magadhesu viharati nālakagāmake."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying in the land of the Magadhans "
"near the little village of Nālaka."

msgctxt "sn38.1:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jambukhādako paribbājako yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the wanderer Jambukhādaka went up to Venerable Sāriputta and exchanged "
"greetings with him."

msgctxt "sn38.1:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho jambukhādako paribbājako āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to Sāriputta:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.252"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn38.1:2.1"
msgid "“‘Nibbānaṃ, nibbānan’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘extinguishment’."

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, āvuso, nibbānan”ti?"
msgstr "What is extinguishment?”"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.3"
msgid "“Yo kho, āvuso, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "“Reverend, the ending of greed, hate, and delusion"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.4"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati nibbānan”ti."
msgstr "is called extinguishment.”"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.5"
msgid ""
"“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa nibbānassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for realizing this "
"extinguishment?”"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.6"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā etassa nibbānassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti."
msgstr "“There is, reverend.”"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.7"
msgid ""
"“Katamo panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā etassa nibbānassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti?"
msgstr "“Well, what is it?”"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.8"
msgid ""
"“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo etassa nibbānassa "
"sacchikiriyāya, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.9"
msgid ""
"sammādiṭṭhi sammāsaṅkappo sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo sammāvāyāmo "
"sammāsati sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.10"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā etassa nibbānassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti."
msgstr "This is the path, the practice, for realizing this extinguishment.”"

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.11"
msgid ""
"“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā etassa nibbānassa sacchikiriyāya."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, this is a fine path, a fine practice, for realizing this "
"extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn38.1:2.12"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti."
msgstr "Just this much is enough to be diligent.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.1:2.13"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
